/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/conic02_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Convex_extra_rewards_are_claimed_to_the/poc_prompt_repair_2.md:25:- claim: Convex reward claims send CRV, CVX, and all extra rewards to the Conic pool address via `getReward(_conicPool, true)`, but the liquidation path only checks `IERC20(rewardToken).balanceOf(address(this))` inside `RewardManagerV2`. Because the RewardManager never receives those extra tokens and has no path to pull arbitrary extra rewards from the pool, listed extra reward tokens accumulate in the pool and are never swapped into CNC.
